(43, 2, 10, 19, 104, 15, 15, NULL, 'Connection of Wine and Joy', 'This connection highlights the theme of wine as a source of joy and gladness in both passages. John 2:10 emphasizes the quality of wine that brings delight, while Psalms 104:15 speaks of wine that ''maketh glad the heart of man.''', 'theme', 0.293, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
